Pearls:  Scriptures to live by...

 
Thousands of Scriptures!
384 Page Book! 
 

  
 PEARLS is a
life-changing book!  From the time-honored wisdom of Solomon, to
the penetrating words of Christ, 
 PEARLS 
is destined to be a classic reference tool and
source of comfort and guidance for life in
the 2000s.  

 
  Compiled by Christian psychologist, Dr. Brian
Campbell, 
 PEARLS
 grew out of Dr. Campbell's need for a
text that would help restore his clients' mental health and provide
needed guidance and comfort in times of crisis.   

   

 
Consisting
entirely of Bible quotations, 
 PEARLS is jam-packed with
over 2,5000 inspirational scriptures for counsel and guidance. 
Arranged alphabetically under 170 topics, 
 PEARLS
is the most comprehensive mental
health Bible concordance ever written.  PEARLS
 is a guiding light for
individuals in all walks of life.  

   

  
PEARLS has
been adopted by Colleges and Seminaries as a tool for training Christian
Counseling.   It's an essential resource for every Christian
counselor and hurting individual.





