Christian Campbell was born on May 12, 1972 in Toronto, Ontario, Canada as Christian Bethune Campbell. He is an actor and producer, known for True Detective (2014), Among Ravens (2014) and Big Love (2006). He has been married to America Olivo since July 5, 2009. He was previously married to Erin Matthews.            
