Suzanne Woods Fisher: Featured Author View More


 Award winning author Suzanne Woods Fisher writes fiction and non-fiction books about faith-based communities. Her interest in the Amish began with her grandfather, who grew up with the Plain, in Pennsylvania. Her newest title The Return, will be released early August.



 

